name: some-javascript-brunch
description: Allows you to make Brunch compile only the javascripts you want.
readme:
Some JavaScript Brunch
======================


In your brunch `config` file, just set the "javascripts" section under "plugins" :

```coffee
  plugins:
    javascripts: [
      'vendor/jquery.js'
      'vendor/bootstrap.js'
    ]
```
